Package org.hibernate.cache.spi

Interface DomainDataRegion

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Region
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractDomainDataRegion, DomainDataRegionImpl, DomainDataRegionTemplate, JCacheDomainDataRegionImpl
    public interface DomainDataRegion
extends Region
    A Region for cacheable domain data - entity, collection, natural-id. Generally speaking, this type of data has: * specific key and value wrapping that needs to be applied * specific access patterns (EntityDataAccess, etc), including some form of locking
